{"tid":1977406,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"軍警以防疫為名殺18平民　高於染疫12死","createTime":"2020-04-18T03:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T04:25:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3287a9f68738541f1f97afb2760ee411703b920","tid":1977406,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情在尼日利亞造成超過400人確診，死亡有12例，但卻傳出尼日利亞負責執行防疫封鎖令的安全部隊，殺死至少18人，比疫情造成的死亡數還多。<br />\n<br />\n尼日利亞國家人權委員會表示，在防疫過程中收到105件安全部隊侵犯人權的投訴，指控尼日利亞安全部隊在執行宵禁期間，造成18名平民死亡，其中8名遭獄警私刑處死，其他2死和軍方有關，另外該國東南部還有1人是被當地委員會殺死，甚至有法外處決的事件發生。<br />\n<br />\n尼日利亞警方表示，封鎖行動是基於專業且符合國際做法，但尼日利亞安全部隊長期被控侵犯人權，他們則駁斥這些指控。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2020/04/17/010146425.shtml</code></pre>"},{"pid":"31fb5926f586bbc4e2750c11de0688c2ccfb7558","tid":1977406,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"子彈療法"},{"pid":"2439803b0e4c95440bde9e2bc349f2d3fbef4df6","tid":1977406,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31fb5926f586bbc4e2750c11de0688c2ccfb7558","tid":1977406,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"子彈療法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:12:40.000Z","msg":"北韓治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1211d7ea6cf018c8f809dacb38674a4b6f92728","tid":1977406,"uid":180404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:12:57.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎疫情在尼日利亞...."},{"pid":"18a938846c5fd2093316995f661278a640efc93c","tid":1977406,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31fb5926f586bbc4e2750c11de0688c2ccfb7558","tid":1977406,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"子彈療法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:25:55.000Z","msg":"鏢靶治療"}]}